OL,3,C"It's next level": Wigan rider
OL,4,Cexplains why he races at the Isle of
OL,5,CMan TT
OL,7,FA TT rider from Wigan has described
OL,8,Fthe Isle of Man event as 'next level'
OL,9,Fand a 'standout fortnight' in the
OL,10,Fworld of road racing.
OL,12,FRob Hodson has been travelling to the
OL,13,Fisland for the TT races his whole
OL,14,Flife, and said "it doesn't really
OL,15,Fstack up to someone who has no
OL,16,Fexperience" of the event.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
