CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780333562
OL,3,C"It's next level": Wigan rider
OL,4,Cexplains why he races at the Isle of
OL,5,CMan TT
OL,7,FHe said: "It's difficult to explain,
OL,8,Fbut, yeah, when you stand on the
OL,9,Fhedges, you know, watching the bikes
OL,10,Fgoing past, you kind of get a, get a
OL,11,Ffeeling of what it's all about and
OL,12,Fwhat the riders must be experiencing."
OL,14,FThe 38-year-old is riding for SMT
OL,15,FRacing, which is also a North West-
OL,16,Fbased team set up in Skelmersdale.
OL,18,FSMT Racing owner, Robin Croft, said:
OL,19,F"This is what we're here for, this is
OL,20,Fwhat we talk about. It's like a
OL,21,Fspiritual home for me, the Isle of Man.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
