OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780333562
OL,3,C"It's next level": Wigan rider
OL,4,Cexplains why he races at the Isle of
OL,5,CMan TT
OL,7,F"It's just a good feeling, everybody's
OL,8,Ffriendly, it's just a great place to
OL,9,Fbe.
OL,11,F"I can't imagine life without it, this
OL,12,Fmy 43rd TT and I never thought I'd be
OL,13,Fsaying that!"
OL,15,FRob added: "You need the people behind
OL,16,Fit to kind of help you out, you know,
OL,17,Forganise it and get it there and set
OL,18,Fit up when you're here, because it's
OL,19,Fnot an easy challenge setting things
OL,20,Flike this up."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
