FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780333562
OL,3,C"It's next level": Wigan rider
OL,4,Cexplains why he races at the Isle of
OL,5,CMan TT
OL,7,FHe concluded: "To do it all with the
OL,8,Fhelp of the team and volunteers and
OL,9,Fthings like that, it means a lot that
OL,10,Fso many people are willing to come and
OL,11,Fhelp me out and help me live my dream,
OL,12,Freally."
OL,14,FThe Isle of Man TT continues this
OL,15,Fweek, ending in the esteemed 6-lap
OL,16,FSenior TT race on Saturday 6 June.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
